      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Add the <strong>onion wedges </strong>to the dish with the <strong>crushed garlic</strong> and cook for 1-2 min</p><p>Whilst the onion and garlic is cooking, drain and rinse the <strong>black beans</strong></p>",
