    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add <strong>half</strong> the<strong> thyme</strong> (stalks and all!) to one side of a<strong> tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray and top with the <strong>chicken breast portions</strong></p><p>Drizzle with <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and sprinkle over the <strong>cayenne pepper </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika </strong>and a<strong> </strong>pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 15 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>Caribbean-style spiced chicken</strong></p>",
