      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into wedges</p><p>Serve the <strong>Caribbean-style spiced chicken</strong> over the <strong>'rice & peas' </strong>with the <strong>spinach</strong> to the side (discard the thyme stems!)</p><p>Drizzle any <strong>remaining chicken juices</strong> over the top and squeeze the<strong> </strong>juice from the<strong> lime wedges</strong> over the rice</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
